data.description: ABSOLUTELY BEAUTIFUL SILVER OAKS VILLAGE HOME! This 3 bedroom 2 bath 1 car garage home has been meticulously maintained. Concrete block constructed in 2001, The roof is new (April 2023), and A/C system 2019. The sellers spare no expense in this outstanding renovation and your home comes with new porcelain title bathrooms, kitchen, floors and exterior paint are all brand new too. Why wait to build when you can have TODAY this adorable, move-in ready. The home has a flowing floorplan as you enter the living room area and adjacent dining room area both with wood flooring installed in July 2023. The kitchen has more than ample cabinet space and features a dinette area as well that overlooks your side pickett in yard. Porcelain tile flooring in the kitchen, baths installed July 2023. Located so close to shopping, retail, medical, and schools. The front wrap around porch is under roof and makes for a great place to relax with your favorite beverage or enjoy an outdoor meal. The Silver Oaks Village is a beautiful community featuring side walks and there is a walking trail that leads straight to the Zephyrhills YMCA. Very, very reasonable HOA dues of only $175 per quarter. This is a beautiful home make it yours today before its gone! Call today!
